						               													<description>You have come to the island in search of revenge against Captain Smith. You believed he died many years ago, but recently evidence surfaced that he may still be alive and hiding here....&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Search for Captain Smith is the second story campaign and expansion for Island Alone. To succeed, players throughout the game must complete the tasks on the campaign cards before the all supplies of food and water run out.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This expansion includes a new map for &amp;quot;The Search for Captain Smith&amp;quot; consisting of 6 parts, new character cards, a goals card, and 9 new campaign objective cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The expansion follows classic gameplay but introduces a few changes and new rules. Instead of one scenario, players complete the objectives from the campaign cards starting with card #1.  Players will encounter outposts guarded by rebels and will need to resolve combat to survive.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
